<taxonomicName id="D4BBDDA70EA9464B5A16C21DB629666D" baseAuthorityName="Faldermann" baseAuthorityYear="1836" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphanes) lucidum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidum" subGenus="Peryphanes">Bembidion (Peryphanes) lucidum</taxonomicName>
(Faldermann, 1836)
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="B5EE53CC422DF83A4FF19BB22F3B40F5" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph id="C5E8DC32B616C4A63333EF2221217DC3" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D568BCB6D4C97886336C681770491662" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<taxonomicName id="24BB6E33F0EE9F6F14AF5964B1114ECF" baseAuthorityName="Faldermann" baseAuthorityYear="1836" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion lucidum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis id="5714297C7AF41EA3177AF34E762F9BFD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Faldermann, 1836 was retained, after a study of the type specimen by 
<bibRefCitation id="849FEE7BD083B9238D772C8E51F7BB6C" DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="41 - 50" refId="B40" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1910. Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion -Arten. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 29: 41 - 50, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" title="Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion - Arten." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" volume="29" year="1910">Netolitzky (1910)</bibRefCitation>
as being very close to 
<taxonomicName id="6268F50E136012B3D628A74E8FF4FDC6" genus="B." lsidName="B. dalmatinum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dalmatinum">
<emphasis id="03B00AD37AAEC34D107B8E2E9B9CFA9F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dalmatinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Dejean, 1831. Later 
<bibRefCitation id="22AD23112972028EE45847DA9B458826" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B42" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1914b. Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10(7/8): 164-176." title="Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10 (7 / 8): 164 - 176." year="1914 b">Netolitzky (1914b)</bibRefCitation>
synonymized 
<taxonomicName id="9224731C214DF6B2364607936FBB7A2A" baseAuthorityName="Faldermann" baseAuthorityYear="1836" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion lucidum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis id="CF4F92BB47A6F5F2A0DC1AA5DAB960C1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<emphasis id="24BE9964DB58AD8B717ADD6C2BEBD784" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<taxonomicName id="4C13089C0E1A1DA2A80FB3CCA24A282F" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1831" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion dalmatinum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dalmatinum">Bembidion dalmatinum</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="92237ADF530B739FEB32A8AE352655CB" authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion fraxator" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fraxator">Bembidion fraxator</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="F9709EA6AD3D0BFDEF7AA5DBB14897BC" originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
, 1832 (currently 
<taxonomicName id="AF3DC9CB80FD699986755EE61B87B6E2" authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion fraxator" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fraxator">
<emphasis id="D3935D28168159F30933C036423449C4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion fraxator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is considered a valid species). 
<bibRefCitation id="F094DE1BA64DC212D7CD71A2E8A50468" author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Apollo Books, Stenstrup" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B28" refString="Marggi, W, Huber, C, Mueller-Motzfeld, G, Hartmann, M, 2003. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242-273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Apollo Books, Stenstrup" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242 - 273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2003">Marggi et al. (2003</bibRefCitation>
: 271) listed 
<taxonomicName id="DCE3F0CD05D9AEE05CC2A0C85A852A4B" genus="B." lsidName="B. lucidum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis id="42978AF0045F7A13FD93D8FA5A21942D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="01C97C98B582BF3BBA6C9E494ECC74CF" genus="B." lsidName="B. dimidiatum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dimidiatum">
<emphasis id="710F3B93D9AF77C4B261B836C56B28B5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dimidiatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="5F3407D88E9703D6F61156BDE4BC82B3" originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
, 1832 which was moved to &quot;incertae sedis&quot;; while the moving of 
<taxonomicName id="C007030F74330BCAEE4D873381685910" genus="B." lsidName="B. dimidiatum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dimidiatum">
<emphasis id="D6570CD27C07F96A8CDABD422FB6C1AE" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dimidiatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was mentioned (p. 21) nothing was stated about 
<taxonomicName id="1B7252C6C6BBAD71C6AA5BC3F12E60FD" genus="B." lsidName="B. lucidum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis id="0675D403176F72B0D2C124212E9D3C04" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This situation remains also in 
<bibRefCitation id="F84730044C2E0A1C7840852881770EE2" author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B29" refString="Marggi, W, Toledano, L, Neri, P, 2017. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294-342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Brill, Leiden" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294 - 342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2017">Marggi et al. (2017)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="10C1887C84A405EDDE3F1892C074946C" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
After having carefully analyzed the literature regarding these taxa (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="6616368C044592E977CB680213AC3226" DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.51784" author="Menetries, E" journalOrPublisher="Academie Imperiale des Sciences, St. Petersbourg" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B30" refString="Menetries, E, 1832. Catalogue raisonne des objets de zoologie recueillis dans un voyage au Caucase et jusqu'aux frontieres actuelles de la Perse. Academie Imperiale des Sciences, St. Petersbourg, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.51784" title="Catalogue raisonne des objets de zoologie recueillis dans un voyage au Caucase et jusqu'aux frontieres actuelles de la Perse." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.51784" year="1832">
<normalizedToken id="A323EB3BF2CB38EE02A429EDC56FE501" originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
1832
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="33F4287F90DF8F60868D08F1465B826F" author="Faldermann, F" journalOrPublisher="Nouveaux Memoires de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes de Moscau" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="1 - 310" refId="B10" refString="Faldermann, F, 1836. Coleoptera Persico Armenica. I. Pentamera (citata anche come: &quot;Fauna Entomologica Tanscaucasica. I&quot;). Nouveaux Memoires de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes de Moscau 4 (1836): 1 - 310" title="Coleoptera Persico Armenica. I. Pentamera (citata anche come: &quot; Fauna Entomologica Tanscaucasica. I &quot;)." volume="4" year="1836">Faldermann 1836</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="D905639E031EABF8698FBAFA98CA6340" author="Schaum, H" journalOrPublisher="Berliner Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="199 - 215" refId="B49" refString="Schaum, H, 1861. Synonymische Bemerkungen. II. Berliner Entomologische Zeitschrift 5: 199 - 215" title="Synonymische Bemerkungen. II." volume="5" year="1861">Schaum 1861</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="974D1AB724C78605B827A1C878C337ED" DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="41 - 50" refId="B40" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1910. Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion -Arten. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 29: 41 - 50, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" title="Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion - Arten." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" volume="29" year="1910">Netolitzky 1910</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="43C7CAD50C6AE5F57964FC6C7DD4EC34" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B42" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1914b. Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10(7/8): 164-176." title="Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10 (7 / 8): 164 - 176." year="1914 b">1914b</bibRefCitation>
; Kryzhanovskij et al. 1995; 
<bibRefCitation id="3A445BF5E857C434DB0C1B97A663D7C3" author="Belousov, IA" journalOrPublisher="Stuttgarter Beitraege zur Naturkunde, (A, Biologie)" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="1 - 40" refId="B4" refString="Belousov, IA, Sokolov, IM, 1996. Review of the Caucasian Species of the subgenus Peryphanes Jeannel (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Bembidion). Stuttgarter Beitraege zur Naturkunde, (A, Biologie) 40 (549): 1 - 40" title="Review of the Caucasian Species of the subgenus Peryphanes Jeannel (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Bembidion)." volume="40" year="1996">Belousov and Sokolov 1996</bibRefCitation>
), we confirm that 
<taxonomicName id="ABD1BA5FBADDD0AE74B9D35F0F88B88B" genus="B." lsidName="B. lucidum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis id="C8C264DBD2FCDA3C4D944D7FBEBBB86B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Faldermann is a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="E42E88522613BB379F6E36552BC7449E" genus="B." lsidName="B. fraxator" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="fraxator">
<emphasis id="FFEDA16076BBB9764183E1E26082958E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. fraxator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="B57465205A778FB5D35CE40B76075A14" originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
and not of 
<taxonomicName id="0C2F2006F098AA7595BFDAEB2CCF9190" genus="B." lsidName="B. dimidiatum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dimidiatum">
<emphasis id="DDD6F7C7D4D9DAB80D832F87F8DAC83D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dimidiatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="0467F81ABE3DE20F69553AC6C45D72E6" originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
, which, moreover, belongs to another subgenus (see above).
</paragraph>
